citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:30 a.m. on
12-Oct-16.
Arrived at the facility at approximately 11:30 a.m., knocked on the door and no one answered. Called the owner and
left a voicemail message and then waited at the facility for 30 minutes.
